<i>noun</i>: 화롯가 [화ː로까/화ː롣까], 난롯가 [날ː로까/날ː롣까] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>화롯가 [화ː로까/화ː롣까]</dt><br>
<dd>1. fireside; beside the fire</dd><br>
<dd>화로의 옆.</dd><br>
<dd>The area around a brazier.</dd><br>
<dd>2. edge of a brazier</dd><br>
<dd>화로의 가장자리.</dd><br>
<dd>The edge of a brazier.</dd><br>
<dt>난롯가 [날ː로까/날ː롣까]</dt><br>
<dd>fireside</dd><br>
<dd>난로의 주변.</dd><br>
<dd>The area around a heater or fireplace.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>